The paper deals with privacy concerns related to data outsourcing in the cloud, which is a common topic in the computer security (cs.CR) sub-category. The proposed mechanism involves data splitting and distributed storage, which are relevant topics in the database (cs.DB) and distributed computing (cs.DC) sub-categories. The paper also emphasizes the importance of efficiency and functionality in cloud computing, which are key topics in the software engineering (cs.SE) and computer architecture (cs.CC) sub-categories.
